column5: My father bought a new Triton and we put it to good use.
those are some dandy bass congats
Those are some chubby Bronze Backs!  Nice job man, keep it up! MTBF
Great lookin smallies!! Are they all from the same body of water?
Thanks guys.Ya most of those ones were from the same lake.
Wow, some fat overfed, greddy obese bass, they need to go on a diet.
Nice smallies! There are some real pigs there. There is something more than a new boat going on there....lots of folks have boats and don't land even one smallie like those. Nice!!
Ya sure put that triton to good use bossman187  Some great looking ones in those pics!!! Thanks for sharing Leechman
The third pic of my dad,that fish was a beast 21x16
Very impressive bunch of smallmouth caught there! Looks like the new boat got some good use.
